# ─── AI Provider (pick ONE — all are free) ────────────────────────────────────

# OPTION 1: Groq — RECOMMENDED (free, fast, no credit card needed)
# Sign up at https://console.groq.com → API Keys → Create key
GROQ_API_KEY=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
# Optional: change model (default: llama-3.1-70b-versatile)
# Other free options: llama-3.1-8b-instant, mixtral-8x7b-32768, gemma2-9b-it
