# OPTION 3: Ollama (100% local, no internet, no API key needed)
# Install from https://ollama.com, then run: ollama pull llama3.1
# Uncomment below after installing:
# OLLAMA_URL=http://localhost:11434
# OLLAMA_MODEL=llama3.1

# OPTION 4: Claude / Anthropic (paid — fallback only)
